</taxonomicName>
L., 
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFEEFF8AFD27FEE4FD51FEA7" box="[714,744,356,382]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="448">Ce</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFEEFF8AFD17FEE4FCD4FEA7" box="[762,877,356,382]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="448">hyalolepis</emphasis>
L. 
